                <h1>About DTRACT</h1>
                <p>The aim of DTRACT is to provide those in need with a platform to organically reduce the amount of time they spend online. Online activity detracts from professional, academic and social capabilities, particularly in young adults. In a world where they're already struggling to balance their activities, activities of this nature can cause potentially irreversible problems.</p>
