            <div class="about_row_left">
                <div class="about_aligner_left">
                    <h1>But Why?</h1>
                    <p>This website was created as a supplication to an MSc. dissertation project investigating the degree to which these aforementioned digital activities negatively imapct aspects of student life, with a particular focus on education and university environments. The application will be accessed by several prospective users over a short-term access period to identify suitaiblity to address the problem at large. This will be achieved by the integration of several interviews to afford the opportunity to collect insightful data into how prospective users felt about DTRACT, along with whether they believe it to be a suitable remedial application to solve the overarching research question. Whilst research into this subject area is plentiful, few go into any real depth to investigate the root cause of the issue, and none of those analysed went further still to design, develop, implement and evaluate a remedial application of this nature. This work will further broaden the knowledge-base of this subject area, providing solid foundation for further work.</p>
                </div>
